{"tid":1997750,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［蘋果好波！］今鑊你哋仲唔冚家剷！！！","createTime":"2020-05-02T01:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T02:55:50.000Z","uid":262250,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"77f20e5b1736c54a252ea4eec92f77a48f6b4c45","tid":1997750,"uid":262250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T01:35:23.000Z","msg":"【醜聞不絕！】警務處助理處長陶輝被揭涉嫌僭建，又涉經營無牌旅館，惟警隊中知法犯法者不獨他一人。本報調查發現，身為警察機動部隊校長的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">莊定賢</span></strong></span>，其住宅一樣涉僭建及霸佔官地；而其花園內竟藏有警察雪糕筒，並另以多個雪糕筒在官地霸佔車位。大律師指，私藏公物已犯下盜竊罪，而用雪糕筒在官地霸佔車位則觸犯《道路交通條例》。另外，曾稱抗爭者為「黃色物體」的新界北總區警司<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">韋華高</span></span>，其住址一樣疑僭建一個面積500呎的天台屋。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200502/NIRONVEY7YHW2FIWKGPE7AOBUY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200502%2FNIRONVEY7YHW2FIWKGPE7AOBUY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw151QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=31ea4732\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200502%2FNIRONVEY7YHW2FIWKGPE7AOBUY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=51b59bfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200502/NIRONVEY7YHW2FIWKGPE7AOBUY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"36f66682e98d9f8f480f554faec0732192b67ebf","tid":1997750,"uid":262250,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T01:38:39.000Z","msg":"你課咗金未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一早課咗啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces